<p>During the building of my blog, I encountered the <strong>command line</strong>. Though solved the tasks at that time, I know nearly nothing about the command line. So today I am going to figure out what the basic command line can do for me.</p>

<p>Due to huge workload and little importance, not grapghs to illustrate.</p>

